## Install on Debian (.deb)

### GPG Key

Add the GPG key of the repository:

```sh
curl -fsSL {{ repo_url }}/{{ repo_name }}.gpg \
  | gpg --dearmor \
  | sudo dd of=/usr/share/keyrings/{{ repo_name }}.gpg
```

### Repository

Add the `.list` file:

```sh
sudo curl --output-dir /etc/apt/sources.list.d -LO {{ repo_url }}/{{ repo_name }}.list
```

### Install

Update then install {{ project_name }}:

```sh
sudo apt update && sudo apt install {{ package_name }}
```

