```sh
sudo curl --output-dir /etc/yum.repos.d -LO {{ repo_url }}/{{ repo_name }}.repo
```

### Install

Install {{ project_name }}:

#### Fedora/RHEL

```sh
sudo dnf install {{ package_name }}
```

#### OpenSuse/Suse

```sh
